<h1>DevPoint Labs Project Manager</h1>

<p>DevPoint Labs coders are constantly working on projects to 1UP their 
coding-ninja skills!
</p>

<p>To help them manage all of these projects, they have 
created this project management application to keep track of their current 
progress and remaining tasks. 
</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Project Name</th>
      <th>Description</th>
      <th>Due Date</th>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= project.name %></td>
        <td><%= project.description %></td>
        <td><%= project.due_date_at.localtime %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Show', project %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_project_path(project) %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', project, method: :delete, 
                                            data: { 
                                              confirm: 'Are you sure you want to delete this project?' } %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>Let's start a <%= link_to 'new project', new_project_path %>!</p>
